OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold on e-bike using his car
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a teenager after driving his
OL,8,Fcar into the e-bike the 15-year-old
OL,9,Fwas riding.
OL,11,FTerrence King, 60, was found guilty of
OL,12,Fkilling Devon Simmonds-Caines after
OL,13,Fdeliberately driving his car into the
OL,14,Fboy on Rowrah Crescent in Manchester.
OL,16,FThe incident took place on 22 July
OL,17,F2025, when King saw Devon on the
OL,18,Fstolen e-bike and, instead of
OL,19,Fcontacting police, steered his vehicle
OL,20,Fdirectly at the teenager at speed
OL,21,Fwithout braking.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
