FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784467108
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold on e-bike using his car
OL,6,FDevon suffered multiple serious
OL,7,Finjuries and despite the efforts of
OL,8,Fparamedics, was pronounced dead at the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FKing was found guilty of murder
OL,12,Ffollowing a trial at Manchester
OL,13,FMinshull Street Crown Court on July
OL,14,F17, 2026.
OL,16,FSobia Ahmed, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService, said: "Terrence King was
OL,18,Fenraged when he saw Devon Simmonds-
OL,19,FCaines on the stolen e-bike.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
