OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784467108
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold on e-bike using his car
OL,6,F"Rather than contacting the police,
OL,7,FKing deliberately took matters into
OL,8,Fhis own hands and drove directly at
OL,9,FDevon, at speed, with fatal
OL,10,Fconsequences.
OL,12,F"He claimed that he had no intention
OL,13,Fto hit the teenager, but this was
OL,14,Frejected by the jury when they found
OL,15,Fhim guilty of murder.
OL,17,F"Devon was a 15-year-old boy with his
OL,18,Fwhole life ahead of him. My thoughts
OL,19,Fare with Devon's parents who must bear
OL,20,Fthis unimaginable loss."
OL,26,@|D@XO]
