PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784467108
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold on e-bike using his car
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer Duncan
OL,7,FThorpe said: "Terrence King
OL,8,Fdeliberately drove his car into Devon,
OL,9,Fcausing traumatic injuries that sadly
OL,10,Fresulted in his death, despite the
OL,11,Fbest efforts of attending emergency
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain with Devon's
OL,15,Ffamily who have had to deal with the
OL,16,Ftrauma following Devon's passing. This
OL,17,Fhas been an incredibly difficult year
OL,18,Ffor Devon's family and friends."
OL,26,@oD@NOUvD@AOUzD@`O]
