PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784467108
OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering 15-year-
OL,4,Cold on e-bike using his car
OL,6,FDuring his police interview, King
OL,7,Fstated that his intention was to block
OL,8,Fthe bike, not to hit Devon, but the
OL,9,Fjury rejected this account.
OL,11,FKing will be sentenced for murder at
OL,12,FMinshull Street Crown Court on 23 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
